{"word":"πλοῦτος","slug":"πλοῦτος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>πλοῦτος, ου, ὁ</el>,</b> also <b><el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:πλοῦτος\">πλοῦτος</a>, τό</el>,</b> but the latter only in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ nom.\">nom.</a> and <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ acc.\">acc.</a> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ Skt.\">Skt.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ assoc.\">assoc.</a>] <b>wealth<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> in material sense <b><a href='B:470 13:22'>Mt 13:22</a>; <a href='B:480 4:19'>Mk 4:19</a>; <a href='B:490 8:14'>Lk 8:14</a>; <a href='B:610 6:17'>1 Ti 6:17</a>; <a href='B:660 5:2'>Js 5:2</a>; <a href='B:730 18:17'>Rv 18:17</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> in non-material sense of abundant supply <b><a href='B:520 2:4'>Ro 2:4</a></b> and <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ oft.\">oft.</a> in the Pauline letters; <b><a href='B:650 11:26'>Hb 11:26</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:πλουτίζω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:πλύνω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}